ailUrl>/RXLImages/1024/34/67/3467Roomthumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>87</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2033</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1024/34/67/3467xml.jpg</Url><Width>180</Width><Height>144</Height><Bytes>7172</Bytes><Caption>xml</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1024/34/67/3467xmlthumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>87</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2350</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Las Madrigueras Hotel and Spa is located in the marvelous setting of the “Golf las Americas” golf course, in Playa de Las Americas, approximately 15 km from the airport. The three storey colonial style hotel blends beautifully into the landscape offering a panoramic view over the golf course and the island of La Gomera. It is an ideal place for a restful and relaxing holiday as many amenities and services are provided. Amongst the facilities are a swimming pool area with a bar, restaurants, a piano bar, a pool room and a magnificent spa. Las Madrigueras Hotel and Spa is an enchanting holiday destination that will provide a magical getaway. Recommended for adults only.

The hotel's Bogey Restaurant was given the award for the Best Hotel Restaurant for 2007 in the Canarias. These awards are annual gastronomic awards running for over 18 years now and preented by the National Canary Island Newspaper Diario de Avisios. The awards were presented by the President of the Canary Island Government earlier this year.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PoliciesDisclaimers</Type><Text>Guests will receive unlimited golf with buggy at Golf Las Americas from 01/05/2009-31/10/2009. During the winter season (01/11/09 - 30/04/09) per room guests will receive a discount of 30% off golf fees with buggy.  Also, there is free use of the gym and SPA with additional charges for treatments.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Hairdresser</Code><Text>Hairdresser</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CloakRoom</Code><Text>Cloak Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantAirconditioned</Code><Text>Restaurant Air-Conditioned</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantNonSmokingArea</Code><Text>Restaurant - non-smoking area</Text></Amenity>